== Logic Setting the [[sample rate]] ==
 




'''1.'''Go to the [[transport]] bar and click and hold on it.

[[image:Logic Customize transport bar.png]]



'''2.'''A menu will appear that says '''customize transport bar'''. Select it and let go of the mouse.




'''3.'''In the window that appears check the box that says '''Sample Rate or Punch Locators''' and click '''OK'''




[[Image:Logic sample rate selector .png]]





'''4.'''In the transport window you should now see the sample rate of your session displayed. Click and hold it to choose a different sample rate.




[[Image:Logic sample rate in transport.png]]



[[Image:Logic Sample rate drop down menu.png]]


